metadata.description:
our home is both a place and dream.
a reality beyond nations where creativity runs wild and free.
a vision of harmony across borders.

welcome tu las californias. 

this mixtape celebrates some of the artists joining us for our first year of this festival (nov. 4/5, 2022). 

1. Joheel Rodmar - El Amor (1ยบ Movimiento)
2. tulengua - purple planets
3. Kamrie - Mental
4. Alec King - Fell In Love 1nce 
5. Yelram Selectah - Mas Melodico
6. Domino - Big Band
7. Sarayu - Nostalgia 
8. Finkel - Nobody Blink
9. Lucid Juice - Rolling High

the border existed in someone's imagination before it became real. 
by inviting musicians and artists from both sides of the wall into one space, 
we melt the border. 
we make it disappear, at least in our relationships. 
slowly, we remember our interdependence. 

community: unity in communication.

this tape is made for anyone who feels their identity is bigger than a box. 
anyone who transcends easy definitions and finds belonging in many labels at once. 
anyone with a borderless spirit. 

we hope you enjoy it. viva la musica. 

cover illustration by bofkid

more info on fest: tulengua.mx/festival-22
